 new brooms, enhance your magic powers, and find the best combination to become the top student!\n\nPlay with the other users in online multiplayer and take in the sight of the world of Little Witch Academia together! \n\n\n\u00a9 2017 TRIGGER / Yoh Yoshinari / \"Little Witch Academia\" Committee \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc.", "short_description": "Soar through the skies, hunt for ghosts, and become the best witch racer in the world!\n\n\u00a9 2017 T/YY/LWAC   \u00a9 UNIV"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Squere_JP_202012.png", "id": "1327244154279833", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982648_1327244157613166_2961322866020914640_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8Jmb_7gjElgQ7kNvgEhQAZ8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A16P0HSVAPGS3HyWPgRMCE5&oh=00_AYCd3wPSXVsRjGQhwnmm0gk__X93sv2SLWDbDwm5V4oEeg&oe=66EC238E"}, {"file_name": "mini_JP_202012.png", "id": "767739813819324", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974453_767739817152657_5763260574459999295_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=OPxjxq5TplQQ7kNvgFlyb1n&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A16P0HSVAPGS3HyWPgRMCE5&oh=00_AYCKK-irXNWSJeW6M7KSHvmjLUZNHT6HKYTiUC-cNMrucg&oe=66EC0E66"}, {"file_name": "Portrait_JP_202012.png", "id": "687368831924916", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974557_687368835258249_3301610840483328822_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EahcAu8ctVkQ7kNvgEW-UfF&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A16P0HSVAPGS3HyWPgRMCE5&oh=00_AYBaYpcsSWmJCPQ8k5yAOOyGjmPN-bnQmdlmfNZf8yPstg&oe=66EC00B3"}, {"file_name": "Landscape_JP_202012.png", "id": "210773470635130", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001687_210773473968463_5238021041892551677_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=oH1_KXMBE4EQ7kNvgHBB782&_nc_ht=scontent.